SELECT A.ELECTRIC_ACCOUNT_ID, A.ELECTRIC_ACCOUNT_SK, ROUND(MONTHS_BETWEEN(LEAST(NVL(A.ACCOUNT_TERMINATED_DTD,SYSDATE),NVL(B.MAX_READING_TO_DT,SYSDATE)), GREATEST(NVL(A.ACCOUNT_OPENED_DTD,SYSDATE),ADD_MONTHS(NVL(B.MAX_READING_TO_DT,SYSDATE),-12)))) AS NUMBER_OF_MONTHS_OPEN, B.BILL_SVC_UNIT_AMT AS ACCOUNT_12_MONTH_REVENUE, B.COMSUMP_TOT_UNITS_QTY AS ACCOUNT_12_MONTH_KWH, B.MAX_PEAK_DEMAND_KW FROM CDM.D_ELECTRIC_ACCOUNT A, (SELECT B1.ELECTRIC_ACCOUNT_SK, MAX(B1.READING_TO_DT) AS MAX_READING_TO_DT, SUM(BILL_SVC_UNIT_AMT) AS BILL_SVC_UNIT_AMT, SUM(CONSUMP_TOT_UNITS_QTY) AS COMSUMP_TOT_UNITS_QTY, GREATEST (MAX (demand_units_on_qty), MAX (demand_units_off_qty)) AS MAX_PEAK_DEMAND_KW FROM CDM.F_ELECTRIC_BILLING B1
WHERE
B1.READING_TO_DT > LAST_DAY(ADD_MONTHS((SELECT MAX(READING_TO_DT) FROM CDM.F_ELECTRIC_BILLING B2 WHERE B1.ELECTRIC_ACCOUNT_SK = B2.ELECTRIC_ACCOUNT_SK AND READING_TO_DT < SYSDATE),-12)) AND B1.READING_TO_DT <= (SELECT MAX(READING_TO_DT) FROM CDM.F_ELECTRIC_BILLING B2 WHERE B1.ELECTRIC_ACCOUNT_SK = B2.ELECTRIC_ACCOUNT_SK AND READING_TO_DT < SYSDATE) GROUP BY B1.ELECTRIC_ACCOUNT_SK) B WHERE A.ELECTRIC_ACCOUNT_SK = B.ELECTRIC_ACCOUNT_SK and A.ACCOUNT_STATUS_ID in ('A', 'P') and A.IS_KEY_ACCOUNT_YN = 'Y'
